=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3ea206179b242ea6688870ec4b240012ff5113","tid":1723330,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:05:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">澄明思諸，勿陷分化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n捉鬼係永遠捉唔完，中共黨史上最叻就係滲透同分化，大家要默認永遠總有隻鬼喺左近，點捉都捉唔曬，過度緊張捉鬼反而會陷入分化局面<br />\n<br />\n平心而論，對家要收風根本唔會帶住支槍，帶得支槍入去理大就擺明預咗比你捉，達成佢地分化你地嘅政治目的，既然有鬼會帶住支槍，冇槍嘅鬼都肯定會有，黑臉白臉嘅鬼自然都會有齊曬，正如連登夠有五毛、TG各公海都一定會有對家臥底，呢個係common sense，所以我再重覆一次，<span style=\"color: red;\">中共黨史上最叻就係滲透同分化，大家要默認永遠總有隻鬼喺左近，點捉都捉唔曬，過度緊張捉鬼反而會陷入分化局面</span>"},{"pid":"3f666f245d4567333cbc5e4a93710e481933d55a","tid":1723330,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"474999e427482ee2da2db2876768a33d3f434026","tid":1723330,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f474e9d68a629f3fa08b27e5bcca8c9243802a61","tid":1723330,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:03:26.000Z","msg":"同意，但下次可唔可以唔好咁老共 style<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:05:00.000Z","msg":"俾啲意見黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />忙中有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:06:46.000Z","msg":"下次再改善啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d427eed8de913f5198e5bce0780d199fdbba332","tid":1723330,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"清楚"},{"pid":"173930aa284cb518b5406ef7b634d5e9beccb2fc","tid":1723330,"uid":221846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:11:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29865aac6438fc